#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/maru.rst:2
msgid "Maru"
msgstr "Maru"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/maru.rst:7
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/maru.rst:9
msgid ""
"`Maru <https://github.com/xcena-dev/maru>`_ is a high-performance KV "
"cache storage engine built on CXL shared memory, designed for LLM "
"inference scenarios where multiple instances need to share a KV cache "
"with minimal latency."
msgstr "`Maru <https://github.com/xcena-dev/maru>`_ 是一个高性能的 KV Cache 存储引擎，基于 CXL 共享内存构建，旨在用于 LLM 推理场景，在这些场景中，多个实例需要以最小延迟共享 KV Cache。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/maru.rst:12
msgid "KV Cache Sharing: Without vs With Maru"
msgstr "KV Cache 共享：没有 Maru 与有 Maru"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/maru.rst:15
msgid ""
"For architecture details, see the `Maru documentation <https://xcena-"
"dev.github.io/maru/>`_."
msgstr "有关架构的详细信息，请参阅 `Maru 文档 <https://xcena-dev.github.io/maru/>`_。"

